high_descs: Turn around the face the white table
Grab the knife off of the table
Turn right and head to the white table
Slice the cabbage on the table with the knife
Turn right and head to the counter to the right of the sink
Place the knife on the counter
Turn around and head to the white table on the left
Grab one of the slices of cabbage
Turn to your left and head to the oven
Place the cabbage in the pot on the stove
Grab the pot off the stove
Turn to your right and stop at the counter to the right of the sink
Place the pot to the right of the knife on the counter
anns.task_desc: Putting a pot with a slice of cabbage in it on the counter

high_descs: Walk to the other side of the white table.
Pick up the butter knife next to the fork.
Turn to the right, walk over to the white table on the other side of the room.
Slice the lettuce on the white table.
Turn to the left, walk to the counter.
Put the butter knife on the counter.
Turn around, cross the room, turn to the table on the left.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn around, cross the room, turn to the left, walk to the stove.
Put the lettuce slice in the pot closest to the sink.
Pick up the pot with the lettuce slice.
Walk to the other side of the sink.
Set the pot to the right of the butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with the lettuce slice on the counter.

high_descs: walk forwards to the wall at the end of the room, then turn right and walk to the wall again, then turn right to face the table
grab the butter knife off of the table
turn right and walk over to the center of the table at the end of the room
slice up the lettuce on the back end of the table
turn left and walk over to the kitchen counter at the end of the room
place the butter knife down on the kitchen counter to the right of the sink
turn around and walk over to the kitchen table on the left side of the room
grab a lettuce slice off of the back side of the table
turn around and walk over to the stove at the end of the room on the right
place the slice of lettuce inside of the pot on the front right burner
take the pot off of the stove with the lettuce piece in it
turn right and walk over to the right side of the kitchen sink on the left
place the pot down on the kitchen counter on the right
anns.task_desc: place a pot with a slice of lettuce in it down on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Walk around to the opposite end of the kitchen table on the right and face the end.
Pick up the knife of the table.
Turn to the right and walk forward to the table across room and face it.
Cut the green vegetable on the table into slices.
Turn to the left and walk forward to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Set the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk halfway across the room, then face the table on the left.
Pick up a slice of the cut vegetable on the table.
Turn around, walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the stove.
Put the slice of vegetable in the pot on the bottom right corner of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the slice of vegetable in it.
Turn to the right, walk across the room and face the counter on the left.
Set the pot with the vegetable in it on the counter to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: To cut a vegetable plus put a slice of it into a pot as well as set the pot on the counter.

high_descs: Walk towards the door then turn right, walk towards the wall then turn right and stand in front of the white table under the window.
Pick up the knife on the table underneath the window.
Turn right then walk across the room towards the white table against the wall.
Cut the cabbage into slices.
Turn left and walk towards the sink.
Place the knife on the right side of the sink on the counter top.
Turn right and walk towards the door, then turn left, stand in front of the white table against the wall.
Pick up a slice of cabbage.
Turn around and walk towards the white table underneath the window, then turn right and walk towards the stove.
Place the slice of cabbage in the pot located on the right front burner of the stove.
Pick up the pot located on the right front burner of the stove.
Turn right and walk towards the microwave, then turn left and stand in front of the counter top.
Place the pot on the right side of the knife on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Cut a slice of cabbage and place it in a pot on the right side of the counter top
